channel.title: Erm need some help, removed the command yet it still works...?
channel.description: using pk planets soruce, i removed ::pure in client.java and before removeing i even tried making it for admins +, i resstarted server and it still works, i dont have a compiler in that folder is that why?

item.title: Erm need some help, removed the command yet it still works...?
item.dc:creator: @starting_coder starting coder
item.description:
@starting_coder wrote:

Copy and paste this into a notepad

@echo off title Server Compiler "C:\Program Files\Java\YOURJAVAVERSION\bin\javac.exe" -cp . *.java pause

Then save the file as Compiler.bat

There, now you have a compiler :]
